data.description: Welcome to your new home sitting on a beautiful peaceful county lot. The main level offers a large eat in country kitchen, living room, family room, bedroom & the primary suite with laundry. Upstairs you will find ample closet space & two additional bedrooms. Enjoy your back covered deck to your fenced in backyard. Explore your property with trails to woods & various fruit trees throughout the property. Make your appointment today to view country living at its finest!
